mmit themselves to the narrow walk of a single sanction honor code in which iron sharpens iron  They embrace the opportunity to hone their integrity  discipline  and civility in a world often lacking these basic qualities  PreparedVMI cadets pursue every opportunity to become worthy of the nation s call for leaders of character  They see a need and endeavor to fill it  FocusedVMI cadets learn to juggle a wide rage of challenges while keeping their eyes on their ultimate goal  to become educated  disciplined  and honorable leaders Home Why VMI Matters Priorities Get Involved About Giving Videos Stories Progress Give  Home Why VMI Matters Priorities Get Involved About Giving Videos Stories Progress Give Home Why VMI Matters Priorities Get Involved About Giving Videos Stories Progress Give Home Home Why VMI Matters Why VMI Matters Priorities Priorities Get Involved Get Involved About Giving About Giving Videos Videos Stories Stories Progress Progress Give Give Traits Traits of a Cadet Preparing young people for lives of service  leadership  and character  SteadfastVMI cadets are faithful to the vision and mission of VMI  committed to reaching for something beyond themselves and dedicated to serving their country and their communities  They stand devoted to an uncommon purpose and a brilliant mission  CourageousVMI cadets choose to stand strong through four years of the adversative VMI system to achieve lofty goals in life  The step forward to grasp a greater understanding of who they are and what they stand for  They take hard strides to reach something of value  DedicatedVMI cadets enter a rigorous academic program where they cannot hide from their professors  They devote themselves to academic pursuits in the face of many other demands  and they succeed  HonorableVMI cadets commit themselves to the narrow walk of a single sanction honor code in which iron sharpens iron  They embrace the opportunity to hone their integrity  discipline  and civility in a world often lacking these basic qualities  PreparedVMI cadets pursue every opportunity to become worthy of the nation s call for leaders of character  They see a need and endeavor to fill it  FocusedVMI cadets learn to juggle a wide rage of challenges while keeping their eyes on their ultimate goal  to become educated  disciplined  and honorable leaders Traits Traits Traits      Traits of a Cadet Preparing young people for lives of service  leadership  and character  SteadfastVMI cadets are faithful to the vision and mission of VMI  committed to reaching for something beyond themselves and dedicated to serving their country and their communities  They stand devoted to an uncommon purpose and a brilliant mission  CourageousVMI cadets choose to stand strong through four years of the adversative VMI system to achieve lofty goals in life  The step forward to grasp a greater understanding of who they are and what they stand for  They take hard strides to reach something of value  DedicatedVMI cadets enter a rigorous academic program where they cannot hide from their professors  They devote themselves to academic pursuits in the face of many other demands  and they succeed  HonorableVMI cadets commit themselves to the narrow walk of a single sanction honor code in which iron sharpens iron  They embrace the opportunity to hone their integrity  discipline  and civility in a world often lacking these basic qualities  PreparedVMI cadets pursue every opportunity to become worthy of the nation s call for leaders of character  They see a need and endeavor to fill it  FocusedVMI cadets learn to juggle a wide rage of challenges while keeping their eyes on their ultimate goal  to become educated  disciplined  and honorable leaders Traits of a Cadet Preparing young people for lives of service  leadership  and character SteadfastVMI cadets are faithful to the vision and mission of VMI  committed to reaching for something beyond themselves and dedicated to serving their country and their communitie